   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="uoedh_hl_h.751_1.jpg"/>

            <opener>


               <address rend="letterhead">
                  <addrLine>LEAGUE FOR PROHIBITION OF CRUEL SPORTS,</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>SOUTH DEVON BRANCH.</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>HON. SECRETARY &amp; TREASURER:</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>WILFRED P. H. WARNER</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>MARLDON</addrLine>
                  <addrLine><choice><abbr>Nr.</abbr><expan>Near</expan></choice>
                     PAIGNTON.</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>DEVON.</addrLine>
               </address>


               <dateline>
                  <date when="1926-10-04">
                     <hi rend="underline">Oct 4<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></hi>
                  </date>
               </dateline>

               <salute>Sir,</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>You will notice by the enclosed card that we are holding an "Anti-Cruel Sport"
               meeting at <placeName ref="#pl:Truro">Truro</placeName>, on the 22<hi
                  rend="superscript">nd</hi>. Would you send us a message of sympathy to be read at
               the meeting. </p>

            <p>I enclose a report of a meeting held at <unclear><placeName ref="#pl:Exeter"
                     >Exeter</placeName></unclear>. </p>

            <closer>
               <salute><choice><abbr>Yrs</abbr>
                     <expan>Yours</expan></choice> faithfully</salute>
               <signed>Wilfred P. H Warner</signed>

               <handShift/>
               <note rend="pencil" hand="#ps:TH">[<choice><abbr>T.O.</abbr>
                     <expan>Turn over</expan></choice> for
                        <choice><abbr>Ans</abbr><expan>Answer</expan></choice>]</note>
            </closer>
            <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.751_2.jpg"/>


         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="reply" hand="#ps:TH">

            <opener>

               <dateline>
                  <date when="1926-10-14">14 Oct. 1926</date>
               </dateline>

            </opener>
            <p> You have all my sympathy in protesting against cruel sports; but I fear that the
               human race has emerged so little yet from a state of savagery that not much can be
               done. </p>
            <closer>
               <signed>T.H.</signed>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </back>
   </text>
